OL,3,CFire service deals with 303 emergency
OL,4,Ccalls as Eleventh Night bonfires are
OL,5,Clit
OL,7,FFirefighters dealt with more than 300
OL,8,Femergency calls as Eleventh Night
OL,9,Fbonfires were lit across Northern
OL,10,FIreland.
OL,12,FIn one incident, firefighters had to
OL,13,Fwithdraw from a bonfire in Cookstown,
OL,14,FCo Tyrone, as a result of a hostile
OL,15,Fcrowd.
OL,17,FIn Belfast, a garage caught fire after
OL,18,Fflames spread from a bonfire.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/9
