OL,3,CFire service deals with 303 emergency
OL,4,Ccalls as Eleventh Night bonfires are
OL,5,Clit
OL,7,FThe burning of Eleventh Night bonfires
OL,8,Fleads to one of the busiest evenings
OL,9,Fof the year for the Northern Ireland
OL,10,FFire and Rescue Service (NIFRS).
OL,12,FArea Commander Dermot Rooney said
OL,13,Foperational activity was "consistently
OL,14,Fhigh" across Saturday night and into
OL,15,FSunday morning.
OL,17,FHe said: "We received 303 emergency
OL,18,Fcalls between the hours of 6pm 11 July
OL,19,Fand 2am 12 July 2026.
OL,26,@uD@ZOUvD@EO]yD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
