CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1783957707
OL,3,CFire service deals with 303 emergency
OL,4,Ccalls as Eleventh Night bonfires are
OL,5,Clit
OL,7,F"This resulted in firefighters
OL,8,Fattending 151 operational incidents `
OL,9,F54 of these were bonfire-related.
OL,11,F"On Milner Street, Belfast,
OL,12,Ffirefighters dealt with a garage fire
OL,13,Ffollowing fire spread from a bonfire.
OL,15,F"In an isolated incident, firefighters
OL,16,Fwithdrew from a bonfire in the
OL,17,FCookstown area as a result of a
OL,18,Fhostile crowd."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUwD@AOUzD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/9
