OL,3,CFire service deals with 303 emergency
OL,4,Ccalls as Eleventh Night bonfires are
OL,5,Clit
OL,7,FMr Rooney said that in Greenisland,
OL,8,Fclose to Carrickfergus in Co Antrim,
OL,9,Ffirefighters dealt with a row of
OL,10,Fterraced houses on fire, along with
OL,11,Ftwo oil tanks and a shed.
OL,13,FHe said: "Two homes were completely
OL,14,Fdestroyed with damage caused to a
OL,15,Ffurther two properties.
OL,17,F"The cause of the fire is under
OL,18,Finvestigation.
OL,26,@uD@JOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/9
