CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1783957707
OL,3,CFire service deals with 303 emergency
OL,4,Ccalls as Eleventh Night bonfires are
OL,5,Clit
OL,7,F"Firefighters also responded to other
OL,8,Fincidents across the night including
OL,9,Faccidental house fires in Antrim and
OL,10,FColeraine and an articulated lorry
OL,11,Ffire in Newry."
OL,13,FHe thanked firefighters, regional
OL,14,Fcontrol centre personnel and support
OL,15,Femployees for delivering the emergency
OL,16,Fresponse.
OL,18,FMr Rooney said: "With further bonfires
OL,19,Fplanned, we are prepared and ready to
OL,20,Frespond to all types of emergencies.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@OO]zD@QOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/9
