OL,3,CFire service deals with 303 emergency
OL,4,Ccalls as Eleventh Night bonfires are
OL,5,Clit
OL,7,F"We would encourage everyone to stay
OL,8,Fsafe and make responsible choices
OL,9,Fthroughout the remainder of the bank
OL,10,Fholiday weekend.
OL,12,F"With warm, dry weather continuing, we
OL,13,Falso ask anyone spending time outdoors
OL,14,Fto follow our countryside fire safety
OL,15,Fadvice."
OL,17,FA number of the traditional Eleventh
OL,18,FNight bonfires were lit across
OL,19,FNorthern Ireland late on Friday and
OL,20,FSaturday, and further pyres will be
OL,21,Fignited on Sunday evening.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUwD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/9
