OL,3,CFire service deals with 303 emergency
OL,4,Ccalls as Eleventh Night bonfires are
OL,5,Clit
OL,7,FThe bonfires are lit ahead of the
OL,8,FOrange Order's July 12 parades across
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland on Monday.
OL,11,FThe parades mark the 334th anniversary
OL,12,Fof the Battle of the Boyne, when the
OL,13,FProtestant King William of Orange
OL,14,Ftriumphed over the Catholic King James.
OL,16,FWhile most of the bonfires pass off
OL,17,Fwithout incident, several have become
OL,18,Fthe focus of contention due to the
OL,19,Fplacing of flags, effigies and
OL,20,Felection posters on the structures
OL,21,Fbefore they are ignited.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/9
