SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F419A1783957707
OL,3,CFire service deals with 303 emergency
OL,4,Ccalls as Eleventh Night bonfires are
OL,5,Clit
OL,7,FThere was widespread condemnation
OL,8,Fafter a bonfire in Moygashel, Co
OL,9,FTyrone, featured a replica of a mosque
OL,10,Fon top.
OL,12,FThat bonfire was lit a day early on
OL,13,FThursday night ahead of a planned
OL,14,Fpolice operation to remove the effigy.
OL,16,FIn Belfast, a man died on Saturday
OL,17,Fafter falling off a bonfire in the
OL,18,FBraniel estate on Friday.
OL,20,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
OL,21,FITVX
